2. ✅ Routing - RESTful endpoint design
3. ✅ Middleware - Cross-cutting concerns
4. ✅ Database - Data persistence
5. ✅ Authentication - Security and user management
6. ✅ Validation - Input sanitization
7. ✅ Error Handling - Robust error management
8. ✅ Testing - Quality assurance
9. ✅ Deployment - Production delivery
10. ✅ Monitoring - Observability and maintenance

